Video Link : https://youtu.be/lrgRCytyeXE


download the chrome driver - the version should match with the version of chrome on your desktop.

here you can find the chrome driver download page : https://googlechromelabs.github.io/chrome-for-testing/
Note : extract the zip in the folder : bharatx/chromedriver-mac-arm64

then activate virtual environment : ```source venv/bin/activate```

download all dependencies using:  ```pip install -r requirements.txt```

then turn on the server : ```python scrape.py```

then : ```curl "http://127.0.0.1:5001/search?product_name=lipstick&location=us"```